Name: Affected by fire
Description: Drainage basin for sample was affected by fire prior to sampling

Name: Algal bloom
Description: Sample potentially affected by the excessive presence of algae

Name: Earthquake
Description: a sudden and violent shaking of the ground, as a result of movements within the earth's crust or volcanic action

Name: Glacial lake outbreak
Description: a sudden release of water (Glacial Lake Outburst) from a lake fed by glacier melt that has formed at the side, in front, within, beneath, or on the surface of a glacier.

Name: Mudflow
Description: a fluid or hardened stream or avalanche of mud.

Name: Storm
Description: a violent atmospheric disturbance, characterized by low barometric pressure, cloud cover, precipitation, strong winds, and possibly lightning and thunder
